Third-party component: axe-core

This plugin runs the axe-core accessibility engine. axe-core is not vendored
into this repository — the a11y-auditor skill loads it from a CDN at runtime,
and the a11y_audit tool pulls it via npm (declared dependency). It is used
unmodified.

